<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>진료 완료 목록 - MediCare+</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
  <script src="/js/feather.min.js"></script>
</head>
<body class="min-h-screen flex">
  {{> common/sidebar-doctor}}

  <div class="main-content flex-1 flex flex-col ml-64">
    {{> common/header-staff}}

    <main class="content-wrapper flex-1 p-6">
      <div class="space-y-6 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-8">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-green-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-green-600">
            <i data-feather="check-circle" class="w-6 h-6"></i>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800">진료 완료 목록</h1>
            <p class="text-slate-500 mt-1">오늘 진료가 완료된 환자 목록입니다.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          {{#reservations}}
            <div onclick="location.href='/doctor/treatment-detail?id={{id}}'"
                 class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 border border-slate-200 transition-all cursor-pointer hover:shadow-md">
              <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-4">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                  <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center bg-green-100 text-green-600">
                    <i data-feather="user" class="w-5 h-5"></i>
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-800 text-lg">{{patientName}}</h3>
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 text-sm text-slate-500 font-medium">
                      <i data-feather="clock" class="w-3.5 h-3.5"></i>
                      {{timeSlot}}
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <span class="px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-bold bg-green-600 text-white">
                  진료 완료
                </span>
              </div>

              <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-3 text-sm text-slate-600 border border-slate-100 line-clamp-2">
                {{note}}
              </div>

              <div class="mt-4 flex justify-between items-center">
                <span class="text-xs font-medium px-2 py-1 rounded-md {{sourceBadgeClass}}">
                  {{sourceText}}
                </span>
                <span class="text-sm font-medium text-green-600 flex items-center gap-1">
                  완료됨 <i data-feather="check-circle" class="w-4 h-4"></i>
                </span>
              </div>
            </div>
          {{/reservations}}
          {{^reservations}}
            <div class="col-span-3 p-8 text-center text-slate-500 bg-white rounded-2xl border border-slate-200">
              진료 완료된 환자가 없습니다.
            </div>
          {{/reservations}}
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>

    {{> common/footer-staff}}
  </div>

  <script>feather.replace();</script>
</body>
</html>
